list.abstract: Personality，英语名词，在英语中有人格、人性、个性等意思。

yingyinNormal.en: The point is the islands of personality are what make Riley, Riley.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要说的是，这些小岛造就了莱莉现有的个性。

yingyinNormal.en: And each core memory powers a different aspect of Riley's personality. Like. Hockey Island.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个核心记忆都会强化莱莉个性的某个方面，比如，冰球岛。

yingyinNormal.en: Eight and a half hours of aptitude tests, intelligence tests, personality tests and what do I learn?
yingyinNormal.zh: 8个半小时的天资测验，智力测验，个性测验，我了解了什么？

yingyinNormal.en: And well, I may not have graduated from here, I admit that my personality is about this Harvard as they come.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我没从这里毕业，我得承认我的个性与哈佛学子的不谋而合。

yingyinNormal.en: Perception of disgust is a combination of variables like age, gender, culture and even personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家对"恶心"的标准不太一样，这些跟年龄、性别、文化甚至是个性有关。

yingyinNormal.en: What are these? Your attribute matrix. It's your personality on a 20-point scale. Like coordination.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些是什么？你的属性矩阵，以20分为满分，定义你的个性，就像坐标一样。

yingyinNormal.en: What's with you? Nothing. It's not suspicious that I'm fixating. It's consistent with my personality. Right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没事吧？没事。我锲而不舍有什么奇怪的，我个性向来坚持不懈。好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Later, the participants read a story about a hypothetical person, and were asked to rate their personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 之后，受试者阅读一篇故事内容关于一个虚构的人物，他们被要求评价这个人物的个性。

yingyinNormal.en: Models in my diner! Oh, no. I wore the wrong sweater vest. You also wore the wrong face, body, and personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 模特来我的餐厅里！惨了，今天穿这件毛衣是错的。你的那张脸，身材与个性也都是错的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not a stranger, we're intellectually compatible, I'm willing to chauffeur you around town, and your personality quirks, which others find abhorrent or rage-inducing, I find cute as a button.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是陌生人，我们的智商又是同一等级，我愿意开车载你满城转，还有你个性怪癖，别人会觉得厌恶或烦人，而我却觉得超级可爱。

yingyinNormal.en: She's part aboriginal, but has a great personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她有部分原住民血统，但是性格真的很好。

yingyinNormal.en: She's great, great looking, great personality, she's greatness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她很棒，长得漂亮，性情好，无可挑剔。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, maybe this is a part of Sheldon's personality he's been repressing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许那是谢尔顿性格中一直被他压抑的一部分。

yingyinNormal.en: Goofball Island? Riley's islands of personality, they're all down. Oh, this is bad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 淘气岛怎么了？莱莉的性格岛，它们都熄灭了，噢，这太糟了。

yingyinNormal.en: I cracked myself up on TV, couldn't stop laughing And my real personality came through.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我曾在电视节目中大笑不止，随后我开始逐渐形成个人的风格。

yingyinNormal.en: Dr. Jekyll's other personality was Mr. Hyde. Mr. Hyde. Didn't have a postgraduate degree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杰基尔博士的另一重人格可是海德先生。海德"先生"啊。他连研究生学位都没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Riley has no core memories. No personality islands and no... Oh. What? What is it? You.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，莱莉失去了核心记忆球，失去了性格岛，也失去了...噢…什么？你说什么？也就失去了你。

yingyinNormal.en: Every movement I made was entirely random, every new personality just on the roll of a dice!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的每一步都是完全随机的，每个新身份都全凭掷骰子决定！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, power of personality. I'm not sure it would've worked for me. Works for me. Are you quite well?
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然是靠人格魅力。这招我恐怕使不来。我就行，你没事吧？

yingyinNormal.en: People are overlooked for a variety of biased reasons and perceived flaws. Age, appearance, personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 球员通常会由于各种偏见和臆断而被埋没，比如年龄，外貌，性格。
